## Forcemap command loc.

forcemap-command-description = Forces the game to start with a given map. Basically sets it in cvar.
forcemap-command-help = forcemap <map ID>
forcemap-command-need-one-argument = forcemap takes one argument, ID of the game map.
forcemap-command-success = Forced the game to start with map { $map }.
forcemap-command-arg-map = <map ID>
